com.sap.spe.pricing.transactiondata

Interface IPricingItemCommon.DynamicReturnContainerConstants

  • Enclosing interface:
    IPricingItemCommon

    public static interface IPricingItemCommon.DynamicReturnContainerConstants
    This class defines all constants, which are used in the dynamic return container. This return container contains key/value pairs determined during the pricing functionality.

    • Field Summary

      Fields 
      Modifier and Type Field and Description
      static java.lang.String PAYMENT_TERM
      key name for payment term (determined by a condition on item level)
      static java.lang.String PAYMENT_TERM_NEW
      key name for the payment term flag, which indicates if the payment term was new determined
      static java.lang.String PAYMENT_TERM_NEW_FALSE
      this value indicates, that the payment term was not new determined
      static java.lang.String PAYMENT_TERM_NEW_TRUE
      this value indicates, that the payment term was new determined
